    "text": "Begin Here Review the Session 2 Deliverables Begin by reviewing how Helena has started organizing her own working system. Use the conversation to resolve questions before building new AI workflows on top of it. Notion workspace Review the Setup Look at how Helena organized pages, views, databases, and daily tasks. Discuss what feels intuitive, what should be simplified, and what could be improved. Task tracking Review Active Marketing Work Review how she is tracking competitive analysis, student campaign research, future marketing ideas, open questions, priorities, statuses, and due dates. Shared drive Review Server Exploration Discuss anything that was difficult to find, folders that were confusing, useful resources she discovered, and suggestions for improving organization. Resource cheat sheet Identify Remaining Gaps Review Helena’s list of key locations and note any missing documentation, unclear ownership, broken links, or folders that still need cleanup before the transition is complete."
