    "url": "modules/session-03.html#deliverables",
    "text": "Session 3 Deliverables Build the PA-AI and RKS Marketing GPTs Use the brand knowledge, files, templates, and AI principles from Sessions 1–3 to build two practical marketing assistants. Deliverable 1 — Build the PA-AI Custom GPT (Guided) Create the PA-AI Marketing GPT using the prepared files and resources. Configure its instructions, knowledge files, conversation starters, and testing prompts. Test it by generating one LinkedIn post. Test it by generating one blog introduction. Test it by generating one YouTube description. Test it by generating one Instagram caption. Document inaccurate, generic, inconsistent, or unclear behavior that should be refined before regular use. Deliverable 2 — Build the RKS Design Custom GPT (Independent) Identify and gather the assets needed to support an RKS Design Marketing GPT. Organize the resources into a clear and logical knowledge base. Create the GPT from scratch using what you learned during the PA-AI walkthrough. Test it by generating copy for multiple marketing formats. Prepare a short rationale explaining why each resource was included. Note any missing resources, unclear rules, or improvements that would strengthen the GPT."
